‚úãüó£Ô∏è Gesture and Voice Command Protocols

All ship functions and nano-ant missions are accessible via hand gestures and verbal commands. Redundancy ensures universal inclusion.

Universal Commands

"Stop" / Raised Hand: Immediate halt of all ant activity.

"Return to Colony" / Circle Gesture: Recall all ants to docking bays.

"Activate Cloak" / Two-Finger Swipe Down: Engage cloaking mode.

"Beacon Mode" / Open Palm Forward: Initiate lighthouse display.

Mission Commands

"Seal the Crack" / Pinch Gesture: Launch minor repair.

"Swap the Tile" / Tap-Tap Motion: Begin tile replacement simulation.

"Check the Vents" / Fan Gesture: Start airflow inspection.

"Emergency Recall" / Fist Clench: Trigger critical ant return.

Accessibility Profiles

Voice-Only Mode: For users with limited mobility.

Gesture-Only Mode: For quiet environments or speech limitations.

Hybrid Mode: Default setting with full redundancy.

